Interface ReplicatedData<K extends java.io.Serializable,V extends java.io.Serializable>

All Known Subinterfaces:
ReplicatedDataWithFailover<K,V>
All Known Implementing Classes:
ReplicatedDataImpl, ReplicatedDataWithFailoverImpl
public interface ReplicatedData<K extends java.io.Serializable,V extends java.io.Serializable>

A container for serializable data, which are replicated in the SLEE cluster, but don't require any failover.

Author:
martins
